<plot>U.S. based Patrick alias Pat decides to act in a Bollywood movie, and travels to Bombay, India. He is met at the airport by prominent and renowed actor Manu Kapoor, the star of this movie, as well as Subramaniam, the director. The first lesson Pat learns the very next morning, is though the scheduled time for the movie to commence shooting is 8:30 AM, no one really shows up until around 11:00 AM. Unfortunately, this will not be the first shock for Pat, as he will find out, when the shooting of this movie starts, and he gets to meet the rest of the caste and crew.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?078208</url></doc>
